  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RETURN TO THE HOUSE WHERE IT ALL BEGAN</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/673df3c8b37d00f1549a54547672ff8d.poster.avif?t=1745426655\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/673df3c8b37d00f1549a54547672ff8d.webm?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/673df3c8b37d00f1549a54547672ff8d.mp4?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>House of Lost Souls</strong> is an atmospheric first-person narrative game where the tragedies of the past come alive within the walls of an old family home. You play as Jack—a man who, years later, returns to the place where he once lost everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long ago, he witnessed the murder of his own parents here. Now, the house calls to him again, feeding on his pain, whispering from the darkness. Memories come alive, twisting into strange and terrifying visions where it’s hard to tell truth from illusion. Yet, it’s within this chaos that Jack must find his answers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/e8c848b784c78fe079cfa1c20b3bb918.poster.avif?t=1745426655\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/e8c848b784c78fe079cfa1c20b3bb918.webm?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/e8c848b784c78fe079cfa1c20b3bb918.mp4?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a slow-burning but deeply unsettling descent into the past, where every step brings you closer to the truth—and to yourself.<br></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person psychological horror with a gripping narrative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a grim family home filled with distorted memories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an atmosphere of fear and isolation, where every sound could be real</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover key items and diary entries from each family member to unravel the secrets of the past</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the protagonist’s inner turmoil and uncover the role his father played in it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Artistic direction and meticulous attention to detail create a chillingly familiar, realistic setting</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RETURN TO THE HOUSE WHERE IT ALL BEGAN</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/673df3c8b37d00f1549a54547672ff8d.poster.avif?t=1745426655\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/673df3c8b37d00f1549a54547672ff8d.webm?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/673df3c8b37d00f1549a54547672ff8d.mp4?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>House of Lost Souls</strong> is an atmospheric first-person narrative game where the tragedies of the past come alive within the walls of an old family home. You play as Jack—a man who, years later, returns to the place where he once lost everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long ago, he witnessed the murder of his own parents here. Now, the house calls to him again, feeding on his pain, whispering from the darkness. Memories come alive, twisting into strange and terrifying visions where it’s hard to tell truth from illusion. Yet, it’s within this chaos that Jack must find his answers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/e8c848b784c78fe079cfa1c20b3bb918.poster.avif?t=1745426655\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/e8c848b784c78fe079cfa1c20b3bb918.webm?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636000/extras/e8c848b784c78fe079cfa1c20b3bb918.mp4?t=1745426655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a slow-burning but deeply unsettling descent into the past, where every step brings you closer to the truth—and to yourself.<br></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person psychological horror with a gripping narrative</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a grim family home filled with distorted memories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an atmosphere of fear and isolation, where every sound could be real</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover key items and diary entries from each family member to unravel the secrets of the past</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the protagonist’s inner turmoil and uncover the role his father played in it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Artistic direction and meticulous attention to detail create a chillingly familiar, realistic setting</p></li></ul>",
